Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:35.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}うしろの正面　{\c&H000000&}この腕を掴むのはだれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:38.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ほら　ほらおいで　{\c&H000000&}踊りましょ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:40.07,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}躊躇{\c&H000000&}いより
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:43.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ほら　ほらおいで　{\c&H000000&}見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.70,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}急ぎた{\c&H000000&}くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:49.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いいよ　{\c&H000000&}慣れない傷も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:54.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}その笑顔が{\c&H000000&}見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:02:00.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願い　願え　{\c&H000000&}終わらせないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:05.05,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君と八百万{\c&H000000&}のぬくもりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:10.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}まとい　捧ぎ　{\c&H000000&}あらがい抱くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}何度でも呼{\c&H000000&}んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}蝶結びア{\c&H000000&}ミュレット
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:20.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}こころ{\c&H000000&}届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:06.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}手指与手指{\c&H000000&}相互触碰维系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:10.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}直到{\c&H000000&}心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:25.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}将用相同的深度　{\c&H000000&}包裹着的世界破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:29.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}现世悄悄地(隐藏起了)　{\c&H000000&}绣球花的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:35.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}后方的正面　{\c&H000000&}抓住这只手的会是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:38.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来　来　过来吧　{\c&H000000&}来跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:40.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}比起{\c&H000000&}犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:43.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来　来　过来吧　{\c&H000000&}去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.70,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}着急{\c&H000000&}更占多数
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:49.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}没事的 {\c&H000000&}不习惯的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:54.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也希望看到{\c&H000000&}那份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:02:00.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}请求　许愿吧　{\c&H000000&}不要让其停下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:05.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}你与无数的{\c&H000000&}温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:10.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}缠绕　奉献　{\c&H000000&}怀着反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}无论多少次{\c&H000000&}都会呼叫呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}蝴蝶结{\c&H000000&}驱魔符
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:20.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}直到{\c&H000000&}心中
