Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是老夫的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在还为时尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视线正如箭雨般地往身上扎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让我们身后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧跟着这样一位金发少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 你能稍微离我们远一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身边的女孩是你的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是外国人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会和你一起来学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an8}是留学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来回答你们的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是当下在世间极具盛名的退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 她乱说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是来学校办事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你带路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请践踏我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「想平凡地活着」我这小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正带着巨大的声响 分崩瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.22,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊的普通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭了「信条杀手」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝·托妮托尔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没有白允许她独自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您当时答应我们无理的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是神的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给我说说那个缠创者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据克拉露丝的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇缠是偶然得到的雷加利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并召唤了高次元体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是她缠创的经过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是召唤高次元体 还是缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该都不是她主动做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我推测是某种外因造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的高次元体级别非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相应的雷加利亚的力量也非常强大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能落入奈兹之手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须由我们回收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的雷加利亚嵌入她体内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她的肉体同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬抢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说是她的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连雷加利亚本身也可能不保
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了弄清奈兹的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们暂时该继续监视和保护皇缠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你的好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱使万千神灵的高次元体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇缠她 为何会有这般强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会想一直待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到命令解除为止都会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭怎么办 你睡哪 换洗衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不用你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问了 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杉並区的女白领被杀事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是受害者的亲人所为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把居住在受害者住处周围的单身人士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挨个问一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本部看起来很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君 这女孩在我们家住一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下 我这就去做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是金发朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法蒂玛亲自出面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 皇缠的安全就得到保障了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 我想趁此机会去调查一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡衣和换的衣服我放这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要把我到家里来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人都会这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的普通和我的普通不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通就是普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给你 尺寸不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她恩将仇报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了由麻以外 她还有这种朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对缠的了解 还是太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做我的护卫我很开心 也很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你能不能穿的低调点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我只有这种法蒂玛发的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你平时不打扮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扮？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真不感兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么可爱真浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在去东京的电车上？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问原因她也不说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要片刻不离地盯着她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本 拥有最多…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发？ 去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去购物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得意忘形 吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我买这么多吃的穿的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没法报答你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用报答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是我们自愿这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的「普通」真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话说 我需要回报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只有克拉露丝你才能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我能做到就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有种非常不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是退魔师的后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不论我怎么跳请神的舞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神都不肯来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资质我是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我能看到普通人看不见的恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想克拉露丝对这方面的事应该很在行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 她是打这个主意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神会来我这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可以检查下你是否能成为缠创者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等的就是你这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明刚才还在开开心心地买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检查有无缠创者的资质很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将封印在这里面的高次元体暂时释放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后看你和它同步程度就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是稍微测试下的话 对身体没有影响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就尽管来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统关闭 限制已解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是克拉露丝的神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被弹开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不同步 应该之会穿过身体才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 麻烦再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻也想要神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输出攻率…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:13:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清玄大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印石…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西碎了就说明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时布下的结界解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻的体内飞出了狸猫和狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高次元体？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的神？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说 我早就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就是退魔少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早已和高次元体同步了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会被弹开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸小狸猫 你们好 我是由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后让我们友好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现状来看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个高次元体虽然早和她同步了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从没有出来过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是被施了某种封印
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却被我的测试给打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长期被封印的高次元体 不知道会做出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造成骚乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常人看不见高次元体 所以肯定会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须快点抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 只有绕到他们前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用问吗 当然是缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 必须这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统关闭 限制已解除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不引起注意 我们从高次元走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也请带上我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高次元体看到你后 可能又会逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我们 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会把他们带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能就这么呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去找那两个神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从他们逃跑的方向来看 应该是这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个女孩怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在录节目还是干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an8}我知道 是网上盛传的退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 大家都在看我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸 小狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们藏到森林里就不好找了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我有个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸最喜欢吃炸豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们用这个引出他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样能引出高次元体？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还很贪吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在 克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是玩偶 被耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高次元体去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 是退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会祛除恶灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别上传
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸 小狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻我 由麻我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求您 请让我见见小狐狸和小狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求您 求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求您 求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:19:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我见见小狐狸和小狸猫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸和小狸猫是不是讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至讨厌到见我就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 就算是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能见到小狐狸和小狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小狐狸和小狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是老夫的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在还为时尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们先留在次元的夹缝之中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸 小狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻我 想和小狐狸小狸猫你们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们愿意和我在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和你们一起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来克拉露丝的笑容是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是她们跳得太奇怪 很好笑罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我就当是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:23:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再次向各位观众宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周开始 本节目将不再是装神少女小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.34,0:24:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而会变成装神少女由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.18,0:24:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻是不会道歉的
